Content:
Multiplies elements in the list.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [1 2 3] | each {|e| 2 * $e }
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ 6 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Produce a list of values in the record, converted to string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
